(lbl : label) (instr : instruction) : if is_label lbl instr then instr = Plabel lbl else instr <> Plabel lbl.
fileSamples.conclusion: if is_label lbl instr then instr = Plabel lbl else instr <> Plabel lbl
fileSamples.proofString:
destruct instr; simpl; try discriminate.
case (peq lbl lbl0); intro; congruence.

(lbl lbl0 : label) : if if peq lbl lbl0 then true else false
then Plabel lbl0 = Plabel lbl
else Plabel lbl0 <> Plabel lbl.
